description: A simple wrapper to apply `List` styles to an `Icon` or `SvgIcon`.
propChildren:
The content of the component, normally `Icon`, `SvgIcon`,
or a `@material-ui/icons` SVG icon element.
propClasses: Override or extend the styles applied to the component.
stylesRoot: Styles applied to the root element.
stylesAlignItemsFlexStart: Styles applied to the root element when the parent `ListItem` uses `alignItems="flex-start"`.
